des:
Are you a huge Toronto Blue Jays fan? Then you need the Jays Journal Flash Briefing Skill by FanSided to get the latest news, opinions and rumors on the Blue Jays. 

Jays Journal is a news and opinion site for fans of the Toronto Blue Jays brought to you by the FanSided Network. Jays Journal is dedicated to providing top-notch Blue Jays news, views, and original content. This site also serves as a community for like-minded fans to come together to catch up on the latest news and to discuss their passion.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
